        "content": "<p>Is there a way to convert from UnitAddCircle to real values from the interval [0, 1) so that some kind of comparison (lt?) is possible?</p>",
        "id": 486129803,
        "sender_full_name": "Ilmārs Cīrulis",
        "timestamp": 1733328870
